---
---

<section class="success-stories reveal" id="work">
    <div class="success-stories__section-label">04 // MISSION LOG</div>

    <div class="success-stories__content">
        <div class="success-stories__cards">
            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-1" style="flex: 0 0 400px;">
                <div class="success-stories__card-header">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Architecture</span>
                    <span class="success-stories__card-id">#MIS-001</span>
                </div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">40% cost reduction</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">SAAS PLATFORM REBUILD</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Architecture overhaul of a multi-tenant SaaS platform serving 200+ enterprise clients. Migrated from monolithic PHP to distributed Node.js, tripling throughput.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-2" style="flex: 0 0 340px;">
                <div class="success-stories__card-header">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Leadership</span>
                    <span class="success-stories__card-id">#MIS-002</span>
                </div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">12-person team</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">SCALE-UP TEAM BUILDING</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Built an engineering team from scratch. Established hiring pipelines, onboarding, and code review culture that cut deploy time from weeks to hours.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-3" style="flex: 0 0 380px;">
                <div class="success-stories__card-header">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Infrastructure</span>
                    <span class="success-stories__card-id">#MIS-003</span>
                </div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">99.99% uptime</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">CLOUD MIGRATION</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Migrated a legacy monolith to cloud-native microservices on AWS — zero downtime, 5M records preserved, 60% infrastructure cost reduction.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-4" style="flex: 0 0 320px;">
                <div class="success-stories__card-header">
                    <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Product Dev</span>
                    <span class="success-stories__card-id">#MIS-004</span>
                </div>
                <span class="success-stories__card-metric">3x conversions</span>
                <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">E-COMMERCE RELAUNCH</h3>
                <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Rebuilt a failing e-commerce platform end-to-end, delivering 3x conversion rate improvement and 60% faster page loads.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="success-stories__cta-row">
            <a class="success-stories__cta" href="#contact">BOOK A CALL</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
    .success-stories {
        position: relative;
        padding: 80px 0 48px 144px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 32px;

        &__section-label {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.6875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--clr-accent);
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        &__content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 48px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        &__cards {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 16px;
            align-items: flex-start;
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding-bottom: 16px;
            padding-right: 48px;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;

            &::-webkit-scrollbar {
                height: 4px;
            }
            &::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
                background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.04);
            }
            &::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
                background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
            }
        }

        &__card {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            background: var(--clr-bg-surface);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            padding: 24px 20px;
            position: relative;

            /* Corner markers */
            &::before, &::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                width: 10px;
                height: 10px;
                border-color: var(--clr-accent);
                border-style: solid;
            }
            &::before {
                top: -1px;
                left: -1px;
                border-width: 2px 0 0 2px;
            }
            &::after {
                bottom: -1px;
                right: -1px;
                border-width: 0 2px 2px 0;
            }
        }

        &__card-header {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        &__card-tag {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.6875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
            color: var(--clr-accent);
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        &__card-id {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.6875rem;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        &__card-metric {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--clr-amber);
            font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
        }

        &__card-title {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 1.2;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        &__card-desc {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: rgba(200, 214, 229, 0.55);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        &__cta-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding-right: 144px;
        }

        &__cta {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
            padding: 14px 40px;
            transition:
                background-color 0.2s ease,
                border-color 0.2s ease;

            &:hover {
                background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
                border-color: var(--clr-accent);
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1440px) {
        .success-stories {
            padding: 64px 0 40px 80px;

            &__cta-row {
                padding-right: 80px;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .success-stories {
            padding: 64px 2rem;

            &__cards {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: stretch;
                overflow-x: visible;
                padding-right: 0;
            }

            &__card {
                flex: none !important;
                width: 100%;
            }

            &__cta-row {
                padding-right: 0;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 375px) {
        .success-stories {
            padding: 64px 1.25rem;

            &__cta-row {
                padding-right: 0;
            }
        }
    }
</style>
